---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 293
  - Title: Srimad Bhagavatam
    Location: XI ii
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=The Spiritual Master
---
O Lord (Krishna), thou art self-effulgent, the embodiment of Truth.
Thou art the Atman, the innermost Self in all beings. Thou art the
teacher of teachers.
